        <para id="id4228945">3. In Activity 1.3 you have had the opportunity to write numbers in expanded notation.  </para>
        <para id="id14037844">See if you can also do it correctly with the following numbers:</para>
        <para id="id15554242">e.g. 26 113 = 20 000 + 6 000 + 100 + 10 + 3</para>
